'''触觉记忆'''（英文： Haptic memory）  是特定于触摸刺激的感觉记忆的形式。在评估抓握熟悉物体并与之互动所需的力时，经常使用触觉记忆。<ref name="Johansson">{{cite journal | title = Memory Representations Underlying Motor Commands Used During Manipulation of Common and Novel Objects | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-neurophysiology_1993-06_69_6/page/1789 | journal = Journal of Neurophysiology | date = 1993-06-15 | last1 = Johansson | last2 = Gordon | last3 =Wrestling | last4=Cole | volume = 69 | issue = 6 | pages = 1789–1796 | doi= 10.1152/jn.1993.69.6.1789| pmid=8350123}}</ref> 类似于视觉[[图像记忆|图像记忆]]，触觉获得的信息的存留是短暂的并且在大约两秒钟后衰减。<ref name="Shih">{{citation | first = Shih | last = Dubrowski, Carnahan | contribution = Evidence for Haptic Memory | title = Third Joint EuroHaptics conference and Symposium on Haptic Interfaces for Virtual Environment and Teleoperator Systems | pages = 145–149 | year = 2009 | doi = 10.1109/WHC.2009.4810867 | isbn = 978-1-4244-3858-7 }}</ref>



